Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Delirious Forsaken', 3: "Don't touch me... Leave me be... I'm fine—I-I'm fine...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Delirious Forsaken', 3: '(Sways back and forth) The Queen... The Queen...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Why would they station so many guards here to watch the humans?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "From the way they look, they're already...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Delirious Forsaken', 3: "Won't do it again... w-won't do it again!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: "I've removed the circular component in gold, which seems to be a piece of hardware-hacking device.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Combat logs of the Goldfinches also show that their hardware was hacked before their M.I.N.D.s were destroyed.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: '...Perhaps all these mechanoid guards are also the victims of the Golden Vortex like these humans.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "I can't do nothing when they're all suffering here.", 4: '1'}
